requests.name: Connections

folders.name: Create
folders.description:
This is query list that you need to add data to the contact list

*   AddContactWithFirstNumber: you can add contact to the list by add input

*   name: string
*   phone_number: string

*   AddNumberToContact: You can add new number for specific contact by add input

*   contact_id: number
*   phone_number: string

folders.name: Delete
folders.description:
This is query list that you need to delete data in the contact list

*   DeleteContactPhone: you can delete specific contact id in the list by add input

*   number: string
*   contact_id: number

folders.name: Edit
folders.description:
This is query list that you need to edit data in the contact list

*   EditContactByID: you can edit specific contact id in the list by add input

*   id: number
*   _set: object

*   EditPhoneNumber: You can add new number for specific contact by add input

*   contact_id: number
*   phone_number: string

folders.name: List
folders.description:
This is query list that you need to get contact list

*   GetContactList: You can get list of contact by hitting this query using parameter limit and offset.

*   Limit: length of phone list you want to get
*   Offset: specific page you want to get

*   GetContactDetail: You can get detail of specific contact by hitting this query with parameter id
*   GetPhoneList: You can get contact list by providing some substrings into the query. We provide these parameters to make it easy

*   where: specific ,
*   distinct_on: ,
*   limit: length of phone list you want to get,
*   offset:specific page you want to get,
*   $order_by
